  "body": "Minor patch release as followup to [0.25](https://github.com/extrawurst/gitui/releases/tag/v0.25.0)\r\n\r\n### Fixes\r\n* bump yanked dependency `bumpalo` to fix build from source ([#2087](https://github.com/extrawurst/gitui/issues/2087))\r\n* pin `ratatui` version to fix building without locked `cargo install gitui` ([#2090](https://github.com/extrawurst/gitui/issues/2090))\r\n\r\n### Support\r\n\r\n[![github](https://img.shields.io/badge/-GitHub%20Sponsors-fafbfc?logo=GitHub%20Sponsors)](https://github.com/sponsors/extrawurst)",
